Sentencas: For the sake of enhance the sinter ability and electrical conductivity of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-& delta; (BZCY) electrolytes, a modified aqueous gel-casting method was applied to synthesize high sintering active and high conductive BZCY nano-powders.
Titulo: Synthesis of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ nano-powders by aqueous gel-casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The new approach makes it easy to obtain pure perovskite.
Titulo: Synthesis of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ nano-powders by aqueous gel-casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The highly sintering active purity-phase of BZCY nano-powder (particle size of 50 & SIM;100 nm) was obtained by calcining at 1100 & DEG;C for 2 h. Nano-powders effectively reduce the sintering densification temperature and successfully prepare BZCY electrolyte with relative density > 96 % at 1450 & DEG;C, and promote grain growth with an average grain size of 2.36 & mu;m.
Titulo: Synthesis of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ nano-powders by aqueous gel-casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Benefiting from this, improved electrical conductivities (e.g., 12.4x10(-3) S cm(-1) at 700 & DEG;C, in wet air) are obtained.
Titulo: Synthesis of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ nano-powders by aqueous gel-casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The NiO-BZCY/BZCY/LSCF-BZCY anode-supporting single cell shows a peak power density of 0.75 W cm(-2) at 700 & DEG;C while taking ambient air as oxidants and wet H-2 (& SIM;3 vol.% H2O) as fuels.
Titulo: Synthesis of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ nano-powders by aqueous gel-casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells
